Subject: Secunia Research: RealPlayer AAC Spectral Data
	Parsing Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 10/12/2010

       - RealPlayer AAC Spectral Data Parsing Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
